sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant BBR as Body Based Router<br/>9004/TCP gRPC/h2 TLS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker<br/>9002/TCP gRPC/h2 TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>Configurable Port
    participant TrainSrv as Latency Training Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant PredSrv as Latency Prediction Server<br/>8001/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request Scheduling (EPP only)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002, TLS (self-signed)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod endpoints + CRD config
    EPP->>ModelServer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP(S), InsecureSkipVerify
    ModelServer-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics<br/>(KV cache, queue depth, running reqs)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc ProcessingResponse<br/>Selected endpoint + headers
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP or gRPC

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: Body-Based Routing (BBR + EPP)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9004, TLS (self-signed)
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps<br/>(bbr-managed=true)
    K8sAPI-->>BBR: Adapter-to-base-model mappings
    BBR-->>Gateway: ext-proc Response<br/>Headers: x-gateway-model-name, x-gateway-base-model
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002, TLS (self-signed)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ext-proc Response<br/>Selected endpoint
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward inference request<br/>to selected model server pod

    Note over EPP,PredSrv: Flow 3: Latency Prediction Training Loop
    EPP->>TrainSrv: POST /train<br/>HTTP/8000, latency observations
    TrainSrv->>TrainSrv: Train ML model<br/>(XGBoost/LightGBM/BayesianRidge)
    TrainSrv-->>TrainSrv: Save model to shared PVC
    PredSrv->>PredSrv: Load model from shared PVC<br/>(sync every 30s)
    EPP->>PredSrv: POST /predict/bulk<br/>HTTP/8001, request features
    PredSrv-->>EPP: TTFT/TPOT predictions
    Note over EPP: Use predictions in<br/>scheduling decisions
